1358
00:57:40,039 --> 00:57:40,759
Where are you from?

1359
00:57:42,599 --> 00:57:43,799
Well, I mean, I'm from...

1360
00:57:45,799 --> 00:57:47,079
Sorry, I like to rest this way.

1361
00:57:52,039 --> 00:57:54,759
Do you feel, Tom, do you feel like they have a secret?

1362
00:57:56,039 --> 00:57:59,879
Yeah, remember they chatted about it last time and they were like,

1363
00:57:59,879 --> 00:58:02,279
oh yeah, see you guys later on the Skype call.

1364
00:58:02,279 --> 00:58:03,639
We're just going to chat for a little bit.

1365
00:58:09,000 --> 00:58:09,559
I'm good.

1366
00:58:09,559 --> 00:58:12,839
Look, next time one of you dies, you can have secret secret meetings too.

1367
00:58:14,039 --> 00:58:15,799
Fine, Russ, I'll hold you that.

1368
00:58:15,799 --> 00:58:18,279
An arrow zips by your head again and says...

1369
00:58:18,920 --> 00:58:21,960
The arrow doesn't say the person you're sh-

1370
00:58:21,960 --> 00:58:24,680
Oh, I thought it was a talking arrow and I was very excited about it.

1371
00:58:27,320 --> 00:58:28,440
Coming in hot.

1372
00:58:28,440 --> 00:58:33,560
Dumbgeons and Dragons is a Dumb Dragons production.
